  </dd>

  <hr /><a name="risingfrom"></a>
  <dt style="font-weight: bold">RISING FROM </dt>
  <dd>See &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dvi6.html#issuant">issuant</a>&rsquo; (also &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dvr2.html#risin">rising 1)</a>&rsquo;. 
  <p>
  <a href="../images/v/vxt-d4674.gif"><img src="../images/v/vxt-d4674.gif" alt="[rising form example]" border="0" height="108" /></a>
  <br /><em>Flag of <a href="ch-ag-sn.html">Schinznach</a>, Switzerland (fotw)</em>
  </dd>

  <hr /><a name="risingsun"></a>
  <dt style="font-weight: bold">RISING SUN </dt>
  <dd>See &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dvr2.html#rising">rising 2)</a>&rsquo;. 
  <p>
